items.badge_description: A global celebration of beer, International Beer Day toasts to beers from all across the globe. Like a helles from Germany, a tripel from Belgian, or an ESB from Britain. Cheers to you, wherever you might be in the world!

Join us to toast glass beer bottles! The U.N. named 2022 the International Year of Glass, recognizing its valuable role in society. Cheers to the sustainable, 100% recyclable glass bottle that keeps beer cold, fresh & delicious. #ChooseGlass
99 bottles of beer on the wall, 99 bottles of beer. Take one down, pass it around.... That's 120 checkins with the serving style of Bottle. Try 5 more for Level 25!
